Pick up the mug on the coffee maker
Turn to your left, move forward then face the fridge on your left side
Open the fridge put in and out the mug then close the fridge

Put the mug on the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left to face the white table.
Take the white mug from the coffee machine on the table.
Turn left, go forward, turn left to face the fridge.
Put the mug on the shelf forward and to the left of the tomato in the fridge. Close and then open the fridge. Take the mug from the fridge.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left to face the white table.
Put the mug on the coffee machine on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the left, head to the kitchen table
Take the white mug from the table
Turn to the left, head to the fridge
Open the fridge door, put the white mug inside. Close the fridge door
wait 7 seconds, open the fridge door, Take the white mug, close the fridge door
head back to the table, put the white mug under the coffee maker
